第十四届全国人民代表大会民族委员会委员职务相应撤销。 值得注意的是，根据全国人民代表大会常务委员会代表资格审查委员会早前报告，由西藏自治区选出的第十四届全国人民代表大会代表，十四届全国人大民族委员会委员，中国医药集团有限公司原总工程师、首席科学家杨晓明，因涉嫌严重违纪违法，2024 年 3 月 29 日，西藏自治区第十二届人大常委会第九次会议决定罢免杨晓明的第十四届全国人民代表大会代表职务。杨晓明被罢免！他带队研发新冠灭活疫苗，曾「以身试药」，9 个月抽约 60 管血 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-67c3d0445ed5296ea44774f4efc47a67_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654316052"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+fiazLWrn7xSEAMaCTEwNzY4MTMwNyDol7SxBjAAOJoFQAVyCTY1NDMxNjA1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1714264311.979991", "card_id": "Q_48938229", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 170}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪部漫画的结局，给你留下的印象最深刻？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "于我而言，其中之一是《幽游白书》。（感谢指正，从小就念成幽灵白书） 这是最后的结局： 看到飘落照片的那一刻，无数情绪涌上心头，怅然若失…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-685b373a53649490a991f26887ca29b4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/48938229"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I+fiazLWrn7xSEAMaCDExNzkxMTE1INrD4LwFMAA4kA1ABnIINDg5MzgyMjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1714264311.981192", "card_id": "Q_654068741", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"